teal.physics.em

Interface GeneratesP

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ConductingSphericalShell, CylindricalMagnet, Dipole, ElectricDipole, GenericPField, InfiniteConductingPlane, LineMagneticDipole, MagneticDipole, PointCharge, PointChargeConductingSphere

    public interface GeneratesP
    Objects that generate a P field should implement GeneratesP. When a World responds to getP requests, it will only sum up the P fields of GeneratesP objects.
